question: In quale fuso orario si trova Salt Lake City?
sparqlQald: PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { res:Salt_Lake_City <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/timeZone> ?uri }
sparql:
PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>
PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/>

}

question: Di quale stato americano Butch Otter è governatore?

question: Quale programma frequent flyer ha la maggior parte delle compagnie aeree?
sparqlQald: SELECT ?uri WHERE { ?airline <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Airline> . ?airline <http://dbpedia.org/property/frequentFlyer> ?uri. } GROUP BY ?uri ORDER BY DESC(COUNT(DISTINCT ?airline)) OFFSET 0 LIMIT 1
sparql:
SELECT ?programFrequentFlyer (COUNT(?airline) as ?count)
WHERE {
   ?programFrequentFlyer rdf:type dbo:Airline_Program .
   ?programFrequentFlyer dbo:operates ?airline .
}
GROUP BY ?programFrequentFlyer
ORDER BY DESC(?count)
LIMIT 1

question: Quale stato americano ha la densità di popolazione maggiore?
sparqlQald: SELECT ?uri WHERE { ?uri <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/country> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States> . ?uri <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/capital> ?capital . ?uri <http://dbpedia.org/property/densityrank> ?density . OPTIONAL {?uri <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> ?string. FILTER (lang(?string) = 'en') } } ORDER BY ASC(?density) LIMIT 1
sparql:
PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>
PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/>

SELECT ?state ?populationDensity
WHERE 
{
  ?state rdf:type dbo:State .
  ?state dbp:populationDensity ?populationDensity .
  FILTER (langMatches(lang(?state), "en") && langMatches(lang(?populationDensity), "en"))
}
ORDER BY DESC(?populationDensity)
LIMIT 1

question: Quanti scienziati si sono laureati in un'Università dell'Ivy League?
sparqlQald: SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?uri) AS ?c) WHERE { ?uri a <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Scientist> ; <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/almaMater> ?university . ?university <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/affiliation> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ivy_League> ; a <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/University> }
sparql:
SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?scientist) AS ?num_scientists)
WHERE {
  ?scientist rdf:type dbpedia-owl:Scientist .
  ?scientist dbpedia-owl:almaMater ?university .
  
  FILTER(?university IN (
    <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Columbia_University>,
    <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brown_University>,
    <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cornell_University>,
    <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dartmouth_College>,
    <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harvard_University>,
    <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Princeton_University>,
    <http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Pennsylvania>,
    <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yale_University>
  ))
}

question: Per quanti anni fu prodotta la Ford T?

  <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ford_Model_T> dbp:productionStartYear ?start .

}

question: Dammi tutti i presidenti americani degli ultimi 20 anni.

sparql:

  ?presidente rdf:type dbpedia-owl:President .
  ?presidente dbpedia-owl:birthPlace dbpedia:United_States .

}

question: Dammi tutti i siti internet di aziende con più di 500000 dipendenti.
sparqlQald: PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT distinct ?web WHERE { ?sub dbo:numberOfEmployees ?obj . ?sub foaf:homepage ?web FILTER( xsd:integer(?obj) > 500000 ) . }
sparql:
SELECT ?azienda ?sito
WHERE {
  ?azienda rdf:type dbo:Company.
  ?azienda dbo:numberOfEmployees ?dipendenti.
  ?azienda foaf:homepage ?sito.
  FILTER (?dipendenti > 500000)
}
